-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kze1665703034325.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kze1665703034325.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kze1665703034325.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kze1665703034325\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                    UDO Characterizations</h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kze1665703034325__ul_qnx_d14_xdc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"chf1665702702105.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/chf1665702702105.html\" title=\"A Many Entity is a Modeled Entity that represents the many side in a one-to-many relationship. It has foreign key fields that match the Primary Key of the One Entity.\">Many Entity</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mgj1665703034608.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mgj1665703034608.html\" title=\"A One Entity is a Modeled Entity that represents the one side in a one-to-many relationship.\">One Entity</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ztg1665703034827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ztg1665703034827.html\" title=\"A non-derived entity is a Component Entity that is created using a template, not a Modeled Entity. It is used to define controls or data that are local to the component and that do not need to be shared with other objects. It is always a non-database entity.\">Non-Derived Entity</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gae1665703035041.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gae1665703035041.html\" title=\"An Outer Entity is a Component Entity that has a child Component Entity. It is part of the data structure of the Component, which determines the access path to the data and the default component processing order and behavior.\">Outer Entity</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tse1665703035180.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tse1665703035180.html\" title=\"An Inner Entity is a Component Entity that has a parent Component Entity. It is used in the data structure of the component, which determines the access path to the data and the default component processing order and behavior.\">Inner Entity</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"liz1665703035686.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/liz1665703035686.html\" title=\"A database entity is an Entity that has its DBMS Path property set to a connector path. It can be mapped to a database table, although it is not necessarily stored in a database.\">Database Entity</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wza1665703030894.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wza1665703030894.html\" title=\"A Non-Database Entity is an Entity that has its Database Behavior property set to F. It can be used to model a group of controls, constant data, derived data, or non-persistent data that do not need to be stored in a database. It cannot be mapped to a database table.\">Non-Database Entity</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"blb1665703026348.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/blb1665703026348.html\" title=\"A non-derived field is a Component Field that has been created from a template, not a Modeled Field. It is always a none-database field, even if its parent is a derived entity.\">Non-Derived Field</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yvz1665702585231.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yvz1665702585231.html\" title=\"A database field is a Modeled Field whose Is External property is True, so it is also known as an external field. It can be used in database I/O.\">Database Field</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dtx1665702585306.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtx1665702585306.html\" title=\"A non-database field is a Modeled Field or Component Field whose Is External property is F. It can be used for a control, constant data, derived data, or other non-persistent data. It cannot be used for database I/O or passing in an entity or occurrence parameter.\">Non-Database Field</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"idk1665702609240.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/idk1665702609240.html\" title=\"An Associated Label belongs to a Component Field. The text of an associated label can be changed using ProcScript.\">Associated Label</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dxr1665702609315.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dxr1665702609315.html\" title=\"A non-associated label is a Label that contains static text that is not associated with a Component Field. It cannot be directly addressed in ProcScript.\">Non-Associated Label</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529452\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529452\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UDO Characterizations Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 UDO Characterizations Many Entity One Entity Non-Derived Entity Outer Entity Inner Entity Database Entity Non-Database Entity Non-Derived Field Database Field Non-Database Field Associated Label Non-Associated Label Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}